{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 4","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada neko priča o svojim kosama, obično govori tri stvari: boja, tip i dužina.</p>\n<p>Boja: Ovo je senka kose. Standardne boje su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">black</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">brown</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">blonde</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">red</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gray</span>.</p>\n<p>Vrsta: Ovo objašnjava kako izgledaju i osećaju se kosa. Vrste kose uključuju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">straight</span> (bez kovrdže), <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wavy</span> (sa blagom kovrdžicom), i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">curly</span> (savijene nadole).</p>\n<p>Visina: Ovo nam govori koliko su krağı. Kosa može biti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">short</span> (iznad ušiju), <span class=\"highlighted-text\">medium</span> (blizu ramena), ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">long</span> (ispod ramena).</p>\n<p>Međutim, na engleskom jeziku, niz pridjeva je važan. Često ćete opisati nečije kose prvo navodeći dužinu, zatim tip, i na kraju boju. Na primer, možete reći da neko ima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">short, curly, blonde hair</span>.</p>\n<p>Sada popuni prazan deo/prostor sa opisom Toma o kosama Lise.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-4"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>She's a colleague with BLANK BLANK BLANK hair and bright brown eyes.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"long","feedback":"<p>Prvo, dužina. Lisina kosa seže ispod ramena.</p>"},{"answer":"wavy","feedback":"<p>Drugo, tip. Lisina kosa ima blage talase dok raste.</p>"},{"answer":"brown","feedback":"<p>Konačno, boja. Kosa Lise je nijansa svetlija od crne, nije ni crna, niti plavokosa.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.3-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":6.52,"finishTimestamp":10.6},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":5.08,"dialogue":{"text":"She's a colleague with long wavy brown hair and bright brown eyes.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":5.58,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","dashedName":"task-4","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-5","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-3","id":"66200a69671a05aa6bcd669e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-in